CS 165 - Project in Algorithms and Data Structures Projects

Spring, 2019

Projects are due by 11:55pm on Fridays and must be turned in electronically. using dropbox on UCI EEE. Project reports must be typed and formatted as a pdf file and source code must be submitted as a single zip file. Handwritten reports or reports in other formats will not be graded.

  • Project 1: Sorting algorithms. Due Friday, April 26, 2019 Monday, April 29, 2019. 100 points.

  • Project 2: Bin-packing algorithms. Due Friday, May 17, 2019 Monday, May 20, 2019. 100 points.

  • Project 3: Graph algorithms. Due Friday, June 7, 2019. 100 points.
